  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Directs that state agencies require that procurement of end point devices be consistent with any relevant standards, guidelines, or guidance developed as part of the National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST) Cybersecurity Framework."
    }
